Equation 2 gives the expected number of new mosquitoes infected by the expected number of birds of species i that became infected by the single infected mosquito in mosquito-to-bird transmission (given by µi in Eq. 1), the sum of which is the R0 of WNV. In Eq. 2, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
